    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trifoil is a minimalistic puzzle game where you draw lines in clever and unconventional ways. Use cryptic symbols to cross, merge, and manipulate lines as you explore a world filled with puzzles and secrets.   <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/extras/06d08b8b1dd4efa1c2b3b1d3e1e81f8c.poster.avif?t=1771330470\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/extras/06d08b8b1dd4efa1c2b3b1d3e1e81f8c.webm?t=1771330470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/extras/06d08b8b1dd4efa1c2b3b1d3e1e81f8c.mp4?t=1771330470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve over 150 meticulously crafted puzzles that gradually unveil the rules, revealing the depth and elegance of the mechanics. As you advance, unexpected twists in the rules challenge you to see the puzzles from a fresh perspective. <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/extras/59187c6bf1235dc2658e3c2fa5278079.poster.avif?t=1771330470\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/extras/59187c6bf1235dc2658e3c2fa5278079.webm?t=1771330470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/extras/59187c6bf1235dc2658e3c2fa5278079.mp4?t=1771330470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 150 handcrafted puzzles, on a smooth difficulty curve, ranging from easy to challenging.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple puzzle symbols, each granting a unique line-drawing ability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several meta mechanics, used in combination with the symbols.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear world to explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secrets and bonus areas.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No annoying tutorials. You discover the Rules as you go.  </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colorblind-friendly visuals. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/extras/8e2af2bd0b5791cd78687a0b7889fd01.poster.avif?t=1771330470\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/extras/8e2af2bd0b5791cd78687a0b7889fd01.webm?t=1771330470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3085710/extras/8e2af2bd0b5791cd78687a0b7889fd01.mp4?t=1771330470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A soothing, dark music and sound effects by Grzegorz Bednorz reflect the mechanics as they are used.<br><br>Join our Discord (link on the right) and become a playtester for the main game!</p>",
